lu.uni.geko.resources
Interface SimpleResourceLoaderExt

All Superinterfaces:
ResourceLoader
All Known Implementing Classes:
DefaultSimpleResourceLoader
public interface SimpleResourceLoaderExt
extends ResourceLoader

The interface to be implemented by clients that extend the extension point lu.uni.geko.resources.simpleresourceloaderext. The extension point allows for simple customisation of the loading and storing process of model resources. In contrast to the extension point RefinedResourceLoaderExt it facilitates extension by giving only control over parts of the process of loading and storing model resources.
